    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/566e17e2485746a0b1d7c9545761f177.poster.avif?t=1741102773\" width=616 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/566e17e2485746a0b1d7c9545761f177.webm?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/566e17e2485746a0b1d7c9545761f177.mp4?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>一触即发</strong>是一款沉浸式的，基于物理的摧毁与建造的游戏。<br>用零件搭建建筑，然后用其撞向你的目标。解锁新的零件，摧毁更多目标，并在数字野兽派的城市风貌中见证彻底的混沌。创造是为了毁灭。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/797703b7b762cf70b35a29d1fb1b51b2.poster.avif?t=1741102773\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/797703b7b762cf70b35a29d1fb1b51b2.webm?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/797703b7b762cf70b35a29d1fb1b51b2.mp4?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造</strong></h2>选择重量、形状和功能各异的零件，建造建筑。<br><br>推进器+连接器+炸弹？那就是一发火箭弹。<br>推进器+旋转器+激光？那就是旋转激光火箭弹。<br>柱+连接器+超重立方体？那就是巨锤。<br><br>零件在手，就天马行空地大干一场，尝试用更少的零件或更有创造力的方式摧毁目标。无论以何种方式摧毁目标，这都会是一道奇观。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/6651900a5c1af6a6a43aea77b008695a.poster.avif?t=1741102773\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/6651900a5c1af6a6a43aea77b008695a.webm?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/6651900a5c1af6a6a43aea77b008695a.mp4?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>摧毁</strong></h2>击中主要目标来赢下战役模式关卡。优先摧毁有护甲的墙壁，这样就可以透过孔洞攻击脆弱的核心。瞄准环境中的炸弹。利用环境中的机制，比如巨大的活塞，来将超重立方体抛向目标。或者就把你拥有的一切砸向目标——说不定也会奏效呢。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/93604aa0d181049a19ce475ad89ca933.poster.avif?t=1741102773\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/93604aa0d181049a19ce475ad89ca933.webm?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/93604aa0d181049a19ce475ad89ca933.mp4?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>复杂的摧毁系统</strong></h2>模拟的静态零件，数千个细小的粒子，庞大的目标灰飞烟灭——而帧率几乎没有浮动。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战役模式</strong></h2>游戏拥有七个世界，每个世界拥有多个关卡，其中包含奖励关卡。每个关卡都有精心设计的可摧毁的城市风貌。每个关卡开始时的零件数目都是有限的，需要您找到利用它们摧毁所有主要方块的途径。随着你的进展，您会解锁新的零件，此外每个世界都有各自独特的环境机制。您随时都可以返回之前的关卡，尝试达到更高的摧毁百分比，或者采用更少的行动将其摧毁。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沙盒模式</strong></h2>尝试新的建造方式。体验尚未解锁的零件。用1000道激光烘烤您的GPU。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新：无尽模式</strong></h2>游玩全新无尽模式，尝试取得终极高分。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>照相模式</strong></h2>用自由移动的摄像头找到最佳的构图角度。暂停画面或给画面减速来抓拍摧毁的瞬间。添加滤镜来改变您照片的意境。导出为无比精细的4K分辨率JPEG。然后与我们分享！<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>支持手柄和重新映射按键</strong></h2>使用手柄掌控局面。当然，所有按键都可设置调整。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可旋转GIF摄像头</strong></h2>创造您自己的完美破坏循环GIF！<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>支持STEAM创意工坊</strong></h2>在本地或Steam创意工坊中安全加载您自己的创作。这可以通过沙盒模式下的自定义UI轻松实现。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/e9f37a11b9aadd9ff67a3ec026d7815c.poster.avif?t=1741102773\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/e9f37a11b9aadd9ff67a3ec026d7815c.webm?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1671480/extras/e9f37a11b9aadd9ff67a3ec026d7815c.mp4?t=1741102773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
